1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the impact of SDMA on spatial throughput in wireless networks, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture.
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the performance of different beamforming techniques, which is related to information theory.
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the use of multiple antennas for enhancing spatial throughput, which is relevant to multimedia applications.
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the impact of network density on spatial throughput, which is related to systems and control.
5. cs.COM (Computers and Society) - Although less likely, the paper could also be relevant to the societal impact of wireless networks and their limitations in ultra-dense small cell networks.
